# Example AGENTS.md Skills File

This file defines agent capabilities and behavioral guidelines.

## Code Review

- Always check for security issues before committing
- Validate all user inputs against schemas
- Use type hints for all function signatures

## File Operations

- Never modify files outside the working directory
- Always create backups before applying patches
- Prefer reading files with line ranges for large files

## Shell Commands

- Timeout all commands to prevent hanging
- Never run destructive commands without confirmation
- Capture both stdout and stderr
